HEADWORD: Whereupon
<hw>Where`up*on"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Upon which; in
consequence of which; after which.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The townsmen mutinied and sent to Essex; <qex>whereupon</qex> he
came thither.</q> <rj><qau>Clarendon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wherever</ent>⟦br⟧
